OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely sunny day across
OL,6,FEngland and Wales with some low cloud
OL,7,Fpotentially affecting western coasts.
OL,8,FCloudier across Scotland and Northern
OL,9,FIreland with some occasional rain but
OL,10,Falso sunny spells. Feeling warm for
OL,11,Fmost and hot towards the southeast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain across the northwest
OL,14,Fmoves southeastwards overnight, but
OL,15,Fweakening as it moves across England
OL,16,Fand Wales. Drier behind with some
OL,17,Fclear spells. Widely mild and staying
OL,18,Fwarm in the southeast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
