OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA largely sunny day,
OL,6,Falthough northwest Scotland, Northern
OL,7,FIreland and some western coasts
OL,8,Felsewhere often cloudier with some
OL,9,Fpatchy drizzle. Another very warm day
OL,10,Ffor most.
